data.description:
This beautifully updated home in the heart of Rocky Hill is a must see!  

You can feel the true ''hominess'' in this house the second you walk through the door! With gorgeous LVP flooring, new windows and fresh paint this bright, airy house welcomes you! Completely renovated kitchen is an absolute STUNNER with white cabinets, granite countertops, tile flooring, all new appliances, walk in pantry, island and breakfast bar.  

There is not a single stitch of carpet in this home either...all newer LVP flooring is throughout the living room, office, dining room, all 4 bedrooms and bonus room.  Beautiful master suite features vaulted ceilings, walk in shower & separate whirlpool tub. 3 other spacious bedrooms PLUS large bonus room, this home has an abundance of space!  Back deck overlooks private backyard.  The secret jewel of this home is the walk-in crawlspace that in no way feels like a crawlspace!  This area is perfect for home gym or man cave or an abundance of storage! 

Lyons Crossing has one of the best neighborhood pools in Knoxville!  This home comes complete with pool membership that is already paid for the year! Also, it is located directly across the street from it making it easy to enjoy a full day of swimming, or a quick dip without the hassle of driving or walking far.  

This home has been well loved, well maintained, gorgeously updated and is in one of the best neighborhoods in the heart of the coveted Rocky Hill community.  It truly has it all!
